===Noun===
'''prion'''

# The [[etiologic]] [[agent]] of [[transmissible spongiform encephalopathy|transmissible spongiform encephalopathies]]. The only [[self-replicating]] cause of [[disease]] known to lack [[nucleic acid]]s.
# A self-propagating alternative [[conformer]] of any protein.

